Class EstimationManagerService

java.lang.Object
  com.ibm.webest.processing.impl.administration.EstimationManagerService
All Implemented Interfaces:
EstimationManagerServiceLocal, EstimationManagerServiceRemote
@DeclareRoles(value={"admin","estimator","manager"})
@RolesAllowed(value={"admin","estimator","manager"})
public class EstimationManagerService
extends java.lang.Object
implements EstimationManagerServiceRemote, EstimationManagerServiceLocal

EstimationManager Organizes the data connected to the Estimations and its calculation process.

Author:
Andre Munzinger, David Dornseifer, Gregor Schumm, Oliver Kreis, Wail Shakir
